text: The Bayer designation ν Coronae Borealis (Nu Coronae Borealis) is an optical pair of stars in the constellation Corona Borealis: *ν1 Coronae Borealis *ν2 Coronae Borealis As of 2011, the pair had an angular separation of along a position angle of 164°. ==References== Coronae Borealis, Nu Category:Corona Borealis Category:Double stars
title: Nu Coronae Borealis
